# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok flying into vietnam for the first time in ## years , colin powell did n't want to miss a thing .
# ::alignments
(w / want-01
      :polarity -
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Colin"
                  :op2 "Powell"))
      :ARG1 (m / miss-02
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (t / thing))
      :time (f / fly-01
            :ARG1 p
            :destination (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Vietnam"))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1
                  :range (m2 / multiple
                        :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (y / year))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a new government began work monday in burkina faso with the arrival of ## new ministers , with only two portfolios assigned to the moderate opposition .
# ::alignments
(b / begin-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)
            :ARG1-of (n / new-01))
      :ARG1 (w / work-01
            :ARG0 g)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday))
      :location (c / city
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Burkina"
                  :op2 "Faso"))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (a / arrive-01
                  :ARG1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (m2 / minister))
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)))
            :manner (a2 / assign-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / portfolio
                        :quant 2
                        :mod (o / only))
                  :ARG2 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (o2 / oppose-01)
                        :ARG1-of (m3 / moderate-03)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok saadi gadhafi tested positive for a performance-enhancing steroid in a doping test after a serie a soccer match , the italian olympic committee said wednesday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Olympic"
                  :op2 "Committee")
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Italy")))
      :ARG1 (t / test-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "saadi"
                        :op2 "Gadhafi"))
            :ARG2 (s2 / steroid
                  :ARG0-of (e / enhance-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / perform-02)))
            :ARG3 (t2 / test-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (d / dope-01)
                  :time (a / after
                        :op1 (m / match-03
                              :mod (s3 / soccer))))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (w / wednesday))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (p / person

                  :op2 "Clinton")

            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (p2 / president))
      :manner r
      :ARG0 p
      :mod (f / front)
      :duration (m / multiple
            :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (m2 / month)))
      :ARG0-of (e / establish-01
            :ARG1 (ii / image
                  :mod (p3 / possible-01
                        :polarity -
                        :mod (s / steady)))))

                        :mod c))

                        :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                              :ARG1 p
                              :ARG2 (r / relative))

                              :location c)))
            :time (a4 / after

                        :ARG0 (e / earthquake
                              :mod (m / massive))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :ARG1 d)
      :ARG3 (t / too)
      :ARG6 (r / repeat-01
            :ARG1 (r2 / remark-01
                  :ARG1 (r3 / recommend-01
                        :ARG1 (s / stick-around-03
                              :ARG0 p

                                    :ARG1 a))
                        :ARG1-of (c / cause-01

                                    :ARG1 (w / weather
                                          :time (m / minute
                                                :mod (a2 / any)))))
                        :ARG2 p)
                  :ARG1-of (f3 / familiarize-01))))

            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)

                  :op1 (m / march-01)))

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Hugo"
                              :op2 "Chavez")

                              :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
                  :ARG1 (p3 / pull-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (e / economy)
                        :ARG2 (r / recession-02)
                        :ARG1-of c3
                        :ARG0 (r2 / revenue
                              :mod (o2 / oil)
                              :ARG1-of (f / fall-01))))))

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :ARG2 (s / shoot-02
                              :ARG0 m
                              :ARG1 (c2 / company
                                    :ARG0-of (p / provide-01
                                          :ARG1 (a3 / abort-01))
                                    :location (s2 / state
                                          :name (n / name
                                                :op1 "Arkansas"))))))
            :ARG1 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG0 m)
            :ARG2 (p2 / press
                  :ARG1-of (a4 / associate-01)))
      :op2 (s3 / say-01
            :ARG0 m
            :ARG1 (r / regret-01
                  :polarity -
                  :ARG0 m)))

                                          :op1 "Vancouver")))

# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Toyota"))
      :ARG1 (p / plan-01
            :ARG1 (b / boost-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (s / sell-01
                        :ARG0 c
                        :ARG1 (v / vehicle
                              :quant 1000000)
                        :location (g / globe)))
            :mod (a2 / ambitious)
            :ARG0-of (d / drive-02
                  :ARG1 (m / message-01
                        :ARG1 (s2 / succeed-01
                              :mod (s3 / stellar)))
                  :ARG2 (h / home)
                  :time (a3 / and
                        :op1 (c2 / close-01
                              :ARG0 (c3 / company
                                    :ARG0-of (r / rival-01
                                          :ARG1 c)
                                    :ARG1-of (t / trouble-01)
                                    :mod (c4 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "U.S.")))
                              :ARG1 (p2 / plant))
                        :op2 (s4 / scale-back-05
                              :ARG0 c3
                              :ARG1 (p3 / produce-01)))))
      :time (w / wednesday))
